  {
    "key": "combat|n_n_i_Eyes_up_here_Rusher_i_The_spy_tosses_her_hair_Are|a6b4e6172b39",
    "original": "\\n\\n<i>“Eyes up here, Rusher.”</i> The spy tosses her hair. Are her cheeks flushed?",
    "translation": "",
